WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 32=

00:01:53.210 --> 00:01:55.290 line:80%
We should also thank Wang Yuanjing.

00:01:55.290 --> 00:01:57.570 line:80%
While practicing refining pills,

00:01:57.570 --> 00:01:59.370 line:80%
he taught me a method to extract

00:01:59.850 --> 00:02:02.820 line:80%
the essence of plants using vapor.

00:02:03.290 --> 00:02:04.780 line:80%
The Night Orchid essence

00:02:04.780 --> 00:02:06.730 line:80%
can permanently sustain the effect.

00:02:13.180 --> 00:02:14.460 line:80%
Done!

00:02:17.740 --> 00:02:18.580 line:80%
Granny,

00:02:18.970 --> 00:02:20.370 line:80%
do you want to leave the marsh?

00:02:22.810 --> 00:02:23.930 line:80%
What is this?

00:02:23.930 --> 00:02:25.300 line:80%
Sticky.

00:02:25.300 --> 00:02:26.410 line:80%
Just drink it.

00:02:27.300 --> 00:02:28.900 line:80%
In half an incense stick's time,

00:02:29.620 --> 00:02:31.300 line:80%
we'll see if it works.

00:02:56.620 --> 00:02:57.780 line:80%
Zhao,

00:02:59.580 --> 00:03:01.370 line:80%
did Mr. Mu

00:03:01.370 --> 00:03:02.900 line:80%
apologize to you later?

00:03:04.970 --> 00:03:06.650 line:80%
He nearly angered me to death.

00:03:06.650 --> 00:03:08.180 line:80%
Still young after all.

00:03:08.650 --> 00:03:11.180 line:80%
Not as good as Master Zhengyang.

00:03:12.020 --> 00:03:13.060 line:80%
Granny Jiang,

00:03:13.690 --> 00:03:16.460 line:80%
how did Master Zhengyang
apologize to my aunt?

00:03:17.650 --> 00:03:19.090 line:80%
He...

00:03:20.620 --> 00:03:21.460 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:03:24.300 --> 00:03:25.140 line:80%
I was wrong.

00:03:25.945 --> 00:03:27.245 line:80%
I'll listen to you in everything.

00:03:29.410 --> 00:03:30.250 line:80%
Pingshu!

00:03:30.460 --> 00:03:31.300 line:80%
Coming!

00:03:38.860 --> 00:03:39.700 line:80%
That's it?

00:03:40.090 --> 00:03:41.780 line:80%
Young couples argue.

00:03:41.780 --> 00:03:43.300 line:80%
It's normal.

00:03:44.180 --> 00:03:45.900 line:80%
Master Zhengyang deserved it.

00:03:46.180 --> 00:03:47.090 line:80%
Men must be taught

00:03:47.410 --> 00:03:49.460 line:80%
when disobedient.

00:03:51.970 --> 00:03:53.340 line:80%
What happened

00:03:53.340 --> 00:03:54.970 line:80%
to them after?

00:03:55.530 --> 00:03:56.580 line:80%
Later,

00:03:57.860 --> 00:04:00.460 line:80%
Aunt found out Master Zhengyang
had deceived her,

00:04:01.210 --> 00:04:02.810 line:80%
and they separated.

00:04:03.410 --> 00:04:04.740 line:80%
Later,

00:04:05.180 --> 00:04:06.740 line:80%
Aunt killed a fiend

00:04:08.180 --> 00:04:09.530 line:80%
and was seriously injured.

00:04:10.300 --> 00:04:11.530 line:80%
Five years ago,

00:04:12.340 --> 00:04:13.490 line:80%
she passed away.

00:04:16.700 --> 00:04:17.540 line:80%
Then,

00:04:18.940 --> 00:04:20.210 line:80%
what happened

00:04:20.820 --> 00:04:22.500 line:80%
between you and Mr. Mu?

00:04:23.410 --> 00:04:24.530 line:80%
We...

00:04:26.610 --> 00:04:27.650 line:80%
can't go back.

00:04:27.970 --> 00:04:29.500 line:80%
If so,

00:04:30.290 --> 00:04:31.700 line:80%
move forward.

00:04:42.820 --> 00:04:43.660 line:80%
Granny,

00:04:44.020 --> 00:04:45.380 line:80%
let me check your pulse.

00:04:48.940 --> 00:04:49.780 line:80%
Granny Jiang,

00:04:50.380 --> 00:04:51.780 line:80%
tell everyone.

00:04:51.780 --> 00:04:53.850 line:80%
You can leave the marsh.

00:04:59.700 --> 00:05:01.020 line:80%
Personally,

00:05:01.340 --> 00:05:02.970 line:80%
this stab brings satisfaction.

00:05:03.530 --> 00:05:04.845 line:80%
This medicine was used by Mr. Mu

00:05:04.856 --> 00:05:06.380 line:80%
to treat your injuries.

00:05:06.650 --> 00:05:08.580 line:80%
Now, returning it settles everything.

00:05:08.580 --> 00:05:09.530 line:80%
What does that mean?

00:05:10.523 --> 00:05:12.596 line:80%
The Young Master considers everything
for Miss Cai.

00:05:12.940 --> 00:05:14.380 line:80%
Now, he's injured,

00:05:14.380 --> 00:05:15.820 line:80%
without a single kind word.

00:05:15.820 --> 00:05:16.862 line:80%
Your Six Sects always say

00:05:16.873 --> 00:05:18.170 line:80%
the Li members are cruel.

00:05:18.170 --> 00:05:19.610 line:80%
You are the truly venomous ones.

00:05:20.970 --> 00:05:21.840 line:80%
How is he?

00:05:21.940 --> 00:05:22.850 line:80%
How is he?

00:05:23.290 --> 00:05:24.780 line:80%
His poison hasn't healed,

00:05:24.780 --> 00:05:25.926 line:80%
and now, he has new injuries.

00:05:26.610 --> 00:05:27.580 line:80%
What do you think?

00:05:31.820 --> 00:05:33.500 line:80%
Since you brought the ointment,

00:05:33.820 --> 00:05:35.140 line:80%
deliver it to him personally.

00:05:36.970 --> 00:05:37.810 line:80%
Fan,

00:05:38.210 --> 00:05:39.530 line:80%
help us get some antidote herbs.

00:05:40.340 --> 00:05:41.210 line:80%
Let's go.

00:05:41.210 --> 00:05:42.820 line:80%
Why? I'm not going.

00:05:43.500 --> 00:05:44.340 line:80%
Go away.

00:05:59.340 --> 00:06:01.153 line:80%
Aren't you supposed to leave
with Song Yuzhi?

00:06:01.940 --> 00:06:03.140 line:80%
Why come back for me?

00:06:03.780 --> 00:06:04.700 line:80%
The Ziwei Method

00:06:05.290 --> 00:06:06.700 line:80%
can confuse the mind,

00:06:07.290 --> 00:06:08.290 line:80%
disrupt the meridians,

00:06:08.900 --> 00:06:09.940 line:80%
and cause sudden death.

00:06:13.340 --> 00:06:14.340 line:80%
You already knew.

00:06:14.780 --> 00:06:16.650 line:80%
Some physicians treating Nie Hengcheng

00:06:17.290 --> 00:06:18.530 line:80%
were loyal to the Mu clan.

00:06:20.050 --> 00:06:21.210 line:80%
So, my father knew

00:06:21.580 --> 00:06:22.900 line:80%
all along.

00:06:23.850 --> 00:06:25.050 line:80%
Yet you still practiced?

00:06:25.050 --> 00:06:26.410 line:80%
Nie Zhe was just a puppet.

00:06:27.380 --> 00:06:28.410 line:80%
The man in black

00:06:28.940 --> 00:06:30.210 line:80%
was the one who killed my father

00:06:31.020 --> 00:06:32.530 line:80%
and Mr. Chang.

00:06:32.780 --> 00:06:34.206 line:80%
I didn't stop you from catching him,

00:06:34.970 --> 00:06:36.012 line:80%
but that doesn't require

00:06:36.023 --> 00:06:37.210 line:80%
the Ziwei Method.

00:06:37.610 --> 00:06:38.730 line:80%
If you keep practicing,

00:06:38.970 --> 00:06:40.243 line:80%
you won't live past three years.

00:06:40.900 --> 00:06:41.970 line:80%
You worry about me?

00:06:48.530 --> 00:06:50.970 line:80%
Are you here to apply medicine to me?

00:06:52.090 --> 00:06:53.810 line:80%
I just don't want
to see you die too early.

00:06:55.410 --> 00:06:56.820 line:80%
With my current injuries,

00:06:56.820 --> 00:06:59.050 line:80%
do you want me
to apply the medicine myself?

00:07:08.900 --> 00:07:11.900 line:80%
Had I known this could keep you,

00:07:14.020 --> 00:07:15.850 line:80%
I should've taken more cuts from you.

00:07:16.290 --> 00:07:17.900 line:80%
Had I known you'd pester me like this,

00:07:19.500 --> 00:07:20.580 line:80%
I'd never have let you

00:07:20.580 --> 00:07:21.653 line:80%
move into Chunling Cottage.

00:07:27.140 --> 00:07:28.090 line:80%
If so,

00:07:30.020 --> 00:07:31.820 line:80%
I wouldn't have worried my parents

00:07:33.290 --> 00:07:34.610 line:80%
or brought shame to the sect.

00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:36.840 line:80%
During this year of confinement,

00:07:37.780 --> 00:07:39.020 line:80%
I often think

00:07:41.340 --> 00:07:42.500 line:80%
that if I hadn't met you,

00:07:43.210 --> 00:07:44.700 line:80%
would I have already been living

00:07:45.580 --> 00:07:46.970 line:80%
the peaceful life

00:07:46.970 --> 00:07:48.500 line:80%
I wanted?

00:07:49.340 --> 00:07:50.970 line:80%
Would I be freer

00:07:52.290 --> 00:07:53.130 line:80%
and happier?

00:07:54.020 --> 00:07:55.050 line:80%
You regret it?

00:07:55.500 --> 00:07:56.970 line:80%
But there's no medicine for regret.

00:07:59.380 --> 00:08:00.700 line:80%
People must pay the price

00:08:00.700 --> 00:08:01.700 line:80%
for their choices.

00:08:02.850 --> 00:08:04.063 line:80%
Seven lashes of the Python Whip

00:08:04.290 --> 00:08:06.500 line:80%
were the price I paid
for defying my sect.

00:08:07.580 --> 00:08:08.730 line:80%
The stab in your chest

00:08:09.820 --> 00:08:11.970 line:80%
is the price you paid for using me.

00:08:13.020 --> 00:08:14.170 line:80%
The Cais

00:08:14.700 --> 00:08:15.700 line:80%
live without regrets.

00:08:16.580 --> 00:08:17.940 line:80%
Love is love.

00:08:18.580 --> 00:08:20.170 line:80%
Hate is hate.

00:08:20.970 --> 00:08:22.500 line:80%
I did love you,

00:08:22.820 --> 00:08:23.970 line:80%
but I loved even more

00:08:24.580 --> 00:08:26.700 line:80%
the person I was when I loved you.

00:08:29.090 --> 00:08:29.930 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:08:31.460 --> 00:08:32.500 line:80%
people can plan,

00:08:33.380 --> 00:08:34.220 line:80%
persist,

00:08:35.410 --> 00:08:36.780 line:80%
and even obsess,

00:08:37.690 --> 00:08:39.170 line:80%
but you must see the cost

00:08:39.170 --> 00:08:40.220 line:80%
behind obsession.

00:08:40.860 --> 00:08:42.500 line:80%
Know when to stop losses.

00:08:42.810 --> 00:08:43.860 line:80%
At least,

00:08:43.860 --> 00:08:46.100 line:80%
know how to protect yourself.

00:08:49.620 --> 00:08:51.290 line:80%
Stop practicing the Ziwei Method.

00:08:54.980 --> 00:08:56.380 line:80%
I'll start over with you.

00:09:08.220 --> 00:09:09.366 line:80%
Hurry! Burn the Night Orchid!

00:09:09.900 --> 00:09:10.740 line:80%
Hurry!

00:09:11.330 --> 00:09:12.530 line:80%
Burn the Night Orchid!

00:09:12.530 --> 00:09:13.620 line:80%
Young Master,

00:09:13.620 --> 00:09:14.620 line:80%
bad news.

00:09:14.631 --> 00:09:16.104 line:80%
Miss Cai is burning the Night Orchid.

00:09:17.810 --> 00:09:19.100 line:80%
I'll definitely burn it.

00:09:19.690 --> 00:09:20.980 line:80%
Even if I die, I'll stop you.

00:09:21.860 --> 00:09:23.050 line:80%
Does the promise you made

00:09:23.050 --> 00:09:24.220 line:80%
still count?

00:09:24.220 --> 00:09:25.220 line:80%
What promise?

00:09:25.220 --> 00:09:27.410 line:80%
If I give up on the Ziwei Method,

00:09:28.050 --> 00:09:29.220 line:80%
you will stay by my side,

00:09:29.740 --> 00:09:30.740 line:80%
as you promised.

00:10:07.100 --> 00:10:09.570 line:80%
Xingjia has land and a shop.

00:10:09.570 --> 00:10:11.100 line:80%
He can take care of you.

00:10:15.380 --> 00:10:16.410 line:80%
Let's go, Granny.

00:10:18.290 --> 00:10:19.130 line:80%
Follow us!

00:10:23.380 --> 00:10:24.330 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:10:24.330 --> 00:10:26.100 line:80%
Yuzhi and I have other matters.

00:10:26.100 --> 00:10:26.986 line:80%
We'll leave first.

00:10:26.997 --> 00:10:28.877 line:80%
Are you going to investigate
the corpse slaves?

00:10:29.220 --> 00:10:30.060 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:10:30.290 --> 00:10:31.450 line:80%
Master will arrive soon.

00:10:32.020 --> 00:10:33.810 line:80%
If he finds Zhao with you,

00:10:33.810 --> 00:10:34.980 line:80%
there will be trouble.

00:10:35.860 --> 00:10:37.450 line:80%
You may not know,

00:10:37.740 --> 00:10:39.020 line:80%
but a year ago, that whipping

00:10:39.410 --> 00:10:40.900 line:80%
almost cost Zhao her life.

00:10:43.570 --> 00:10:45.020 line:80%
This is our Six Sects' matter.

00:10:47.220 --> 00:10:48.140 line:80%
You need not worry.

00:10:48.650 --> 00:10:49.490 line:80%
Farewell.

00:10:54.700 --> 00:10:57.300 line:80%
(Guangtian Sect, Desheng Hall)

00:11:00.980 --> 00:11:02.020 line:80%
There's no proof.

00:11:02.650 --> 00:11:03.620 line:80%
We should get evidence

00:11:04.020 --> 00:11:05.220 line:80%
before seeing Master.

00:11:05.500 --> 00:11:06.650 line:80%
You wretched girl.

00:11:06.930 --> 00:11:08.330 line:80%
What are you thinking?

00:11:09.330 --> 00:11:10.860 line:80%
You haven't married Song,

00:11:11.050 --> 00:11:12.150 line:80%
yet you disobey your father.

00:11:12.530 --> 00:11:13.370 line:80%
Who taught you?

00:11:14.220 --> 00:11:16.290 line:80%
Grandfather just died,

00:11:16.290 --> 00:11:17.980 line:80%
yet Father told me to marry Song Xiuzhi

00:11:17.980 --> 00:11:19.690 line:80%
and forced me to poison him secretly.

00:11:20.170 --> 00:11:21.450 line:80%
I can't obey.

00:11:22.170 --> 00:11:24.140 line:80%
If I can't control you,

00:11:24.140 --> 00:11:25.410 line:80%
your father will.

00:11:26.450 --> 00:11:27.290 line:80%
Who?

00:11:30.100 --> 00:11:30.940 line:80%
Go.

00:11:34.340 --> 00:11:35.300 line:80%
(Rainlight Chamber)

00:11:35.330 --> 00:11:37.740 line:80%
Song Xiuzhi isn't simple either.

00:11:39.690 --> 00:11:40.530 line:80%
Wretched girl.

00:11:40.780 --> 00:11:42.220 line:80%
Ungrateful like her mother.

00:11:42.500 --> 00:11:44.500 line:80%
We must use the Control Powder

00:11:44.500 --> 00:11:45.930 line:80%
to make her obedient.

00:11:46.500 --> 00:11:48.570 line:80%
She'll have to drug him.

00:11:50.450 --> 00:11:51.290 line:80%
Master You,

00:11:51.650 --> 00:11:52.570 line:80%
why are you here?

00:11:52.570 --> 00:11:53.410 line:80%
Mr. Song,

00:11:53.810 --> 00:11:55.380 line:80%
don't think we were following you.

00:11:55.690 --> 00:11:57.450 line:80%
To be clear, we arrived first.

00:11:57.810 --> 00:11:58.650 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:11:58.787 --> 00:12:00.667 line:80%
the Young Master has questions
for Yang Heying.

00:12:00.810 --> 00:12:01.763 line:80%
We just arrived as well.

00:12:02.380 --> 00:12:03.220 line:80%
Lord Yang.

00:12:04.170 --> 00:12:05.010 line:80%
Mu...

00:12:07.740 --> 00:12:08.580 line:80%
Chief Mu.

00:12:08.860 --> 00:12:09.700 line:80%
Lord Yang,

00:12:10.140 --> 00:12:11.050 line:80%
long time no see.

00:12:11.780 --> 00:12:13.048 line:80%
Last year's plan to capture you

00:12:13.059 --> 00:12:14.220 line:80%
was not my idea.

00:12:14.220 --> 00:12:15.530 line:80%
Every debt has its debtor.

00:12:15.530 --> 00:12:16.450 line:80%
Don't act rashly.

00:12:16.450 --> 00:12:17.860 line:80%
Last year, I was caught

00:12:17.860 --> 00:12:19.220 line:80%
because I was outmatched.

00:12:19.220 --> 00:12:20.290 line:80%
I have nothing to say.

00:12:20.930 --> 00:12:22.050 line:80%
Today, I didn't come

00:12:22.050 --> 00:12:23.100 line:80%
for revenge.

00:12:23.740 --> 00:12:25.860 line:80%
I just have two questions for you.

00:12:26.330 --> 00:12:29.050 line:80%
Speak truthfully,

00:12:31.410 --> 00:12:32.780 line:80%
and I won't kill anyone.

00:12:34.020 --> 00:12:34.946 line:80%
What are the questions?

00:12:35.530 --> 00:12:37.140 line:80%
What happened to the corpse slaves

00:12:37.740 --> 00:12:39.380 line:80%
near Guangtian Sect?

00:12:39.620 --> 00:12:40.675 line:80%
Isn't making corpse slaves

00:12:40.686 --> 00:12:42.450 line:80%
a secret of your sect?

00:12:42.450 --> 00:12:43.410 line:80%
How would I know?

00:12:43.650 --> 00:12:44.490 line:80%
If you want answers,

00:12:44.620 --> 00:12:45.930 line:80%
you should ask Song Shijun.

00:12:46.860 --> 00:12:49.100 line:80%
The play you and Song Xiuzhi staged

00:12:49.410 --> 00:12:50.810 line:80%
was impressive.

00:12:51.290 --> 00:12:53.290 line:80%
But you missed one key point:

00:12:53.690 --> 00:12:54.690 line:80%
I've killed all

00:12:54.690 --> 00:12:56.620 line:80%
of Nie Zhe's subordinates

00:12:56.930 --> 00:12:58.780 line:80%
who knew the corpse slave method.

00:12:59.650 --> 00:13:00.530 line:80%
Speak!

00:13:00.530 --> 00:13:01.650 line:80%
Was it Yu Huiyin

00:13:03.100 --> 00:13:04.650 line:80%
or the man in black?

00:13:05.450 --> 00:13:07.100 line:80%
I don't know what you're saying.

00:13:08.220 --> 00:13:09.060 line:80%
Guanyue.

00:13:10.100 --> 00:13:10.940 line:80%
He's asking for me.

00:13:14.930 --> 00:13:16.100 line:80%
Evil will be punished by evil.

00:13:16.450 --> 00:13:17.290 line:80%
Your gentlemanly act

00:13:17.290 --> 00:13:18.380 line:80%
is useless on them.

00:13:18.900 --> 00:13:20.020 line:80%
Since they're willing to act,

00:13:20.410 --> 00:13:21.650 line:80%
let them question first.

00:13:22.570 --> 00:13:23.410 line:80%
Young Master.

00:13:24.870 --> 00:13:25.740 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:13:25.740 --> 00:13:26.740 line:80%
What do you want?

00:13:26.740 --> 00:13:27.820 line:80%
- Chief Mu.
- Tianci.

00:13:27.820 --> 00:13:28.670 line:80%
Chief Mu.

00:13:28.680 --> 00:13:30.140 line:80%
Honey, just speak.

00:13:30.140 --> 00:13:31.690 line:80%
Saving the child comes first.

00:13:32.450 --> 00:13:33.380 line:80%
Chief Mu,

00:13:33.900 --> 00:13:35.810 line:80%
I don't know anything

00:13:35.810 --> 00:13:37.140 line:80%
about Yu or Nie.

00:13:37.290 --> 00:13:38.170 line:80%
You don't have

00:13:38.170 --> 00:13:40.330 line:80%
to falsely pin the corpse slaves on me.

00:13:40.780 --> 00:13:41.620 line:80%
Lord Yang,

00:13:41.980 --> 00:13:43.100 line:80%
don't regret this later.

00:13:44.280 --> 00:13:45.140 line:80%
Mr. Mu, you're asking

00:13:45.140 --> 00:13:46.530 line:80%
about six months ago, right?

00:13:47.140 --> 00:13:47.980 line:80%
Six months ago,

00:13:48.570 --> 00:13:49.740 line:80%
Father suddenly cleared

00:13:49.740 --> 00:13:51.450 line:80%
a secluded yard behind the mountain.

00:13:51.450 --> 00:13:52.380 line:80%
Soon after,

00:13:52.380 --> 00:13:54.620 line:80%
villagers went missing repeatedly,

00:13:54.620 --> 00:13:56.290 line:80%
causing widespread panic.

00:13:56.290 --> 00:13:58.450 line:80%
The villagers asked Father
to investigate.

00:13:58.450 --> 00:14:00.060 line:80%
He agreed in words,

00:14:00.060 --> 00:14:00.930 line:80%
but the next day,

00:14:00.930 --> 00:14:02.570 line:80%
the yard

00:14:02.570 --> 00:14:04.860 line:80%
was burned completely.

00:14:04.860 --> 00:14:07.100 line:80%
Mother, for some reason, went there

00:14:07.100 --> 00:14:08.500 line:80%
and was gravely injured.

00:14:09.930 --> 00:14:10.770 line:80%
She...

00:14:11.170 --> 00:14:13.050 line:80%
She died from pain.

00:14:13.450 --> 00:14:15.050 line:80%
So, they previously experimented

00:14:16.050 --> 00:14:18.450 line:80%
on nearby villagers.

00:14:18.450 --> 00:14:19.930 line:80%
Sensing trouble,

00:14:19.930 --> 00:14:21.330 line:80%
they destroyed the evidence

00:14:21.330 --> 00:14:22.780 line:80%
and moved the corpse slave workshop

00:14:22.780 --> 00:14:24.500 line:80%
to a more remote Mount Qimu.

00:14:24.500 --> 00:14:26.140 line:80%
I've always wanted to know, Father:

00:14:26.740 --> 00:14:28.330 line:80%
What happened in that yard?

00:14:28.330 --> 00:14:30.050 line:80%
Why did Mother go there?

00:14:30.810 --> 00:14:32.740 line:80%
If you made the corpse slaves

00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:34.860 line:80%
and killed my grandfather,

00:14:35.170 --> 00:14:37.570 line:80%
uncles, aunts, and cousins?

00:14:37.570 --> 00:14:38.780 line:80%
Girl, stop spouting nonsense.

00:14:40.380 --> 00:14:41.220 line:80%
Lord Yang,

00:14:42.290 --> 00:14:44.100 line:80%
you know what I'm capable of.

00:14:44.530 --> 00:14:45.650 line:80%
My arrival means

00:14:45.650 --> 00:14:47.100 line:80%
I already know

00:14:47.100 --> 00:14:48.170 line:80%
the facts.

00:14:49.290 --> 00:14:50.810 line:80%
Why still deny it?

00:14:51.330 --> 00:14:52.810 line:80%
If you know everything,

00:14:53.140 --> 00:14:54.450 line:80%
why ask me?

00:14:55.690 --> 00:14:57.810 line:80%
You killed Grandfather?

00:14:58.650 --> 00:14:59.570 line:80%
What about Mother?

00:15:00.450 --> 00:15:02.290 line:80%
Was her death truly accidental?

00:15:03.930 --> 00:15:04.770 line:80%
Guanyue.

00:15:09.170 --> 00:15:10.010 line:80%
Little one,

00:15:10.220 --> 00:15:13.380 line:80%
come with me for candy.

00:15:13.380 --> 00:15:14.330 line:80%
I don't want candy!

00:15:14.330 --> 00:15:15.450 line:80%
I don't!

00:15:15.450 --> 00:15:16.530 line:80%
- Mother!
- Tianci!

00:15:16.530 --> 00:15:17.380 line:80%
Honey,

00:15:18.690 --> 00:15:20.020 line:80%
just say it.

00:15:20.020 --> 00:15:21.530 line:80%
Tianci is your only heir.

00:15:21.530 --> 00:15:23.290 line:80%
Nothing can happen to him.

00:15:28.690 --> 00:15:30.380 line:80%
Six months ago, someone came to me

00:15:30.780 --> 00:15:32.380 line:80%
and taught me the corpse slave method.

00:15:32.810 --> 00:15:34.570 line:80%
I only tried it out of curiosity

00:15:34.570 --> 00:15:35.780 line:80%
and never used it

00:15:35.780 --> 00:15:36.740 line:80%
on your sect.

00:15:37.220 --> 00:15:38.473 line:80%
This has nothing to do with you.

00:15:38.570 --> 00:15:39.410 line:80%
Who was he?

00:15:39.610 --> 00:15:41.496 line:80%
I couldn't recognize him
with his face covered.

00:15:41.810 --> 00:15:42.690 line:80%
Chief Mu,

00:15:42.690 --> 00:15:44.290 line:80%
our Six Sects and your sect

00:15:44.290 --> 00:15:45.740 line:80%
mind our own business.

00:15:46.380 --> 00:15:48.020 line:80%
I advise you not to interfere.

00:15:48.290 --> 00:15:49.483 line:80%
You refined the corpse slaves.

00:15:49.810 --> 00:15:51.330 line:80%
Why frame my father?

00:15:51.530 --> 00:15:52.690 line:80%
You almost killed him!

00:15:55.410 --> 00:15:56.860 line:80%
Song Shijun,

00:15:56.860 --> 00:15:58.740 line:80%
taking your wealth for granted,

00:15:58.740 --> 00:16:00.530 line:80%
looked down on our Siqi Sect

00:16:01.860 --> 00:16:03.530 line:80%
and humiliated me repeatedly.

00:16:04.620 --> 00:16:06.100 line:80%
I finally had a chance to see

00:16:06.100 --> 00:16:07.570 line:80%
his two sons fight.

00:16:07.570 --> 00:16:09.050 line:80%
Why shouldn't I act?

00:16:09.050 --> 00:16:10.020 line:80%
How involved

00:16:10.530 --> 00:16:11.980 line:80%
was Song Xiuzhi in all this?

00:16:12.810 --> 00:16:14.140 line:80%
Your brother

00:16:14.810 --> 00:16:16.530 line:80%
truly hid his nature.

00:16:16.860 --> 00:16:18.380 line:80%
Even I almost misjudged him.

00:16:18.490 --> 00:16:19.410 line:80%
I only wanted

00:16:19.410 --> 00:16:20.930 line:80%
to strengthen Siqi Sect

00:16:20.930 --> 00:16:22.100 line:80%
and vent some anger.

00:16:22.690 --> 00:16:23.740 line:80%
But your brother,

00:16:23.740 --> 00:16:24.930 line:80%
my good son-in-law,

00:16:25.450 --> 00:16:27.330 line:80%
has ambitions far beyond mine.

00:16:27.330 --> 00:16:28.810 line:80%
Lord Song's skills

00:16:28.810 --> 00:16:29.780 line:80%
are far above yours.

00:16:30.610 --> 00:16:31.500 line:80%
How did you plant

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:32.620 line:80%
the Puppet Gu on him?

00:16:33.100 --> 00:16:34.290 line:80%
Who really acted?

00:16:36.330 --> 00:16:37.930 line:80%
Mr. Mu, since you're here,

00:16:38.170 --> 00:16:39.410 line:80%
why not step out?

00:16:43.170 --> 00:16:44.010 line:80%
Zhao,

00:16:44.290 --> 00:16:45.130 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:16:45.570 --> 00:16:46.410 line:80%
come out.

00:16:46.810 --> 00:16:47.650 line:80%
With me here,

00:16:47.900 --> 00:16:48.930 line:80%
he won't dare abduct you.

00:17:00.450 --> 00:17:01.410 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:17:02.380 --> 00:17:03.740 line:80%
long time no see.

00:17:04.020 --> 00:17:04.860 line:80%
Master.

00:17:05.660 --> 00:17:06.500 line:80%
Are you alright?

00:17:06.700 --> 00:17:07.860 line:80%
- I'm fine.
- Master,

00:17:08.460 --> 00:17:09.562 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is investigating

00:17:09.573 --> 00:17:10.700 line:80%
the corpse slaves with us.

00:17:11.180 --> 00:17:12.020 line:80%
This matter

00:17:12.460 --> 00:17:13.530 line:80%
was orchestrated

00:17:14.610 --> 00:17:16.700 line:80%
by Yang Heying and my brother.

00:17:16.980 --> 00:17:17.820 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:17:18.420 --> 00:17:19.570 line:80%
That fiend threatened me

00:17:19.570 --> 00:17:20.610 line:80%
with my wife and child;

00:17:20.610 --> 00:17:22.420 line:80%
I only told lies to stall him.

00:17:22.420 --> 00:17:23.850 line:80%
Changing words again.

00:17:23.850 --> 00:17:24.810 line:80%
You're talking nonsense.

00:17:27.220 --> 00:17:28.060 line:80%
Xiuzhi,

00:17:29.570 --> 00:17:31.220 line:80%
do you have anything to say?

00:17:31.220 --> 00:17:32.060 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:17:32.940 --> 00:17:34.530 line:80%
don't fall for the demonic sect's trap.

00:17:35.090 --> 00:17:36.130 line:80%
How could I harm Father?

00:17:37.370 --> 00:17:38.210 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:17:38.460 --> 00:17:39.693 line:80%
repel the outside threat first.

00:17:39.850 --> 00:17:40.879 line:80%
Don't let the demonic sect

00:17:40.890 --> 00:17:42.570 line:80%
mock the Six Sects.

00:17:42.740 --> 00:17:44.050 line:80%
Xiuzhi is right.

00:17:45.220 --> 00:17:46.060 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:17:46.290 --> 00:17:48.180 line:80%
your father's life is uncertain.

00:17:48.460 --> 00:17:50.290 line:80%
Do we fight each other

00:17:50.290 --> 00:17:52.050 line:80%
in front of the demonic sect?

00:17:53.780 --> 00:17:54.660 line:80%
Master Xiuzhi,

00:17:55.090 --> 00:17:57.610 line:80%
Yang Heying already admitted it.

00:17:57.850 --> 00:17:59.220 line:80%
You're involved

00:17:59.220 --> 00:18:00.780 line:80%
with that fiend.

00:18:00.780 --> 00:18:02.142 line:80%
You worked with the demonic sect,

00:18:02.153 --> 00:18:03.570 line:80%
making my husband admit it.

00:18:03.890 --> 00:18:05.940 line:80%
You traitorous little girl!

00:18:08.700 --> 00:18:10.290 line:80%
Speak nonsense again,

00:18:11.290 --> 00:18:12.500 line:80%
and face the consequences.

00:18:16.290 --> 00:18:17.130 line:80%
Master,

00:18:19.090 --> 00:18:20.420 line:80%
handling sect matters is urgent.

00:18:21.020 --> 00:18:22.046 line:80%
Don't bother with him now.

00:18:23.370 --> 00:18:24.730 line:80%
- Alright.
- Lord Qi,

00:18:25.460 --> 00:18:26.780 line:80%
we can't let them go.

00:18:26.780 --> 00:18:28.330 line:80%
You can clarify

00:18:28.330 --> 00:18:30.180 line:80%
how Leader Huang actually died.

00:18:30.180 --> 00:18:32.290 line:80%
What? As I already said,

00:18:32.290 --> 00:18:34.050 line:80%
it was just to deceive the fiend.

00:18:34.050 --> 00:18:35.460 line:80%
How would I know the truth?

00:18:37.090 --> 00:18:38.940 line:80%
But the day you came to confront,

00:18:38.940 --> 00:18:41.600 line:80%
you spoke as if you saw
Lord Song kill him.

00:18:41.600 --> 00:18:42.450 line:80%
Oh,

00:18:42.450 --> 00:18:43.700 line:80%
you also said

00:18:43.700 --> 00:18:46.570 line:80%
Lord Song hurt Master Xiuzhi.

00:18:46.570 --> 00:18:47.740 line:80%
You depicted

00:18:47.740 --> 00:18:49.220 line:80%
the story vividly,

00:18:49.220 --> 00:18:50.370 line:80%
as if you saw it.

00:18:50.810 --> 00:18:51.810 line:80%
I felt strange.

00:18:52.180 --> 00:18:53.530 line:80%
It's supposed to be a secret.

00:18:54.700 --> 00:18:56.700 line:80%
Lord Yang, how did you know?

00:18:58.090 --> 00:18:59.330 line:80%
Song Xiuzhi told me.

00:18:59.330 --> 00:19:00.180 line:80%
Ask him.

00:19:00.180 --> 00:19:01.780 line:80%
His injuries can't be fake.

00:19:02.220 --> 00:19:03.060 line:80%
Lord Yang,

00:19:04.220 --> 00:19:05.530 line:80%
Father injured me by mistake,

00:19:06.220 --> 00:19:07.570 line:80%
but I never said

00:19:07.570 --> 00:19:09.420 line:80%
he killed Leader Huang.

00:19:09.420 --> 00:19:10.610 line:80%
You told me Father killed

00:19:11.130 --> 00:19:12.740 line:80%
Leader Huang's whole family.

00:19:12.980 --> 00:19:14.050 line:80%
I didn't believe it,

00:19:14.610 --> 00:19:16.180 line:80%
but you made me confront him.

00:19:16.440 --> 00:19:17.290 line:80%
In hindsight,

00:19:17.290 --> 00:19:19.420 line:80%
Father's actions were strange.

00:19:19.780 --> 00:19:20.620 line:80%
Lord Yang,

00:19:20.980 --> 00:19:22.020 line:80%
what exactly did you do

00:19:22.366 --> 00:19:23.786 line:80%
that made Father suddenly attack me?

00:19:24.460 --> 00:19:26.290 line:80%
Good, Song Xiuzhi.

00:19:26.700 --> 00:19:28.370 line:80%
You wiped yourself clean.

00:19:28.780 --> 00:19:30.740 line:80%
If not for letting you become the Lord,

00:19:30.740 --> 00:19:32.090 line:80%
why bother?

00:19:33.090 --> 00:19:34.220 line:80%
I'm Father's eldest son,

00:19:34.940 --> 00:19:36.290 line:80%
qualified to be the Lord.

00:19:37.810 --> 00:19:39.460 line:80%
No need for your scheming.

00:19:39.850 --> 00:19:40.780 line:80%
Song Xiuzhi...

00:19:41.180 --> 00:19:42.020 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:19:42.460 --> 00:19:43.740 line:80%
your brother

00:19:43.740 --> 00:19:44.940 line:80%
has a great talent

00:19:45.500 --> 00:19:46.500 line:80%
for acting.

00:19:49.090 --> 00:19:50.180 line:80%
If you had clarified things

00:19:50.180 --> 00:19:51.810 line:80%
in person that day,

00:19:52.209 --> 00:19:53.688 line:80%
things wouldn't have become like this.

00:19:53.780 --> 00:19:55.130 line:80%
I didn't expect that Sha Tian'er

00:19:55.610 --> 00:19:56.940 line:80%
would suddenly attack Father.

00:19:58.180 --> 00:19:59.940 line:80%
He must have been misled.

00:20:00.660 --> 00:20:02.530 line:80%
Thinking of the massacre,

00:20:02.850 --> 00:20:04.090 line:80%
he was enraged,

00:20:04.460 --> 00:20:06.050 line:80%
wanting to repay with his life.

00:20:06.050 --> 00:20:08.420 line:80%
Sha Tian'er wasn't a Huangsha member.

00:20:11.980 --> 00:20:12.820 line:80%
Ungrateful girl.

00:20:14.020 --> 00:20:14.890 line:80%
Lord Qi.

00:20:18.700 --> 00:20:20.460 line:80%
This is the Huangsha disciple registry.

00:20:21.090 --> 00:20:22.780 line:80%
Grandfather didn't have many disciples.

00:20:22.780 --> 00:20:24.420 line:80%
I know each of them,

00:20:24.420 --> 00:20:25.740 line:80%
but I've never heard

00:20:26.610 --> 00:20:28.330 line:80%
of Sha Tian'er.

00:20:29.330 --> 00:20:30.500 line:80%
So,

00:20:30.500 --> 00:20:31.700 line:80%
Sha Tian'er

00:20:31.700 --> 00:20:33.700 line:80%
was probably a trained assassin.

00:20:34.290 --> 00:20:35.610 line:80%
That day, I found it odd:

00:20:36.290 --> 00:20:37.780 line:80%
He was weak

00:20:37.780 --> 00:20:38.980 line:80%
but fearless.

00:20:38.980 --> 00:20:40.330 line:80%
Such determination

00:20:40.330 --> 00:20:41.530 line:80%
is beyond normal people.

00:20:42.290 --> 00:20:43.850 line:80%
If not for real hatred,

00:20:44.180 --> 00:20:45.810 line:80%
he must be trained since childhood.

00:20:48.180 --> 00:20:49.020 line:80%
Lord Yang,

00:20:50.420 --> 00:20:52.370 line:80%
why send assassins to kill my father?

00:20:53.940 --> 00:20:55.306 line:80%
I was deceived by Song Xiuzhi,

00:20:55.317 --> 00:20:57.700 line:80%
only aiming to avenge
my father-in-law and brothers-in-law.

00:20:57.700 --> 00:20:58.850 line:80%
You're lying.

00:20:58.850 --> 00:21:00.940 line:80%
You despised Mother
for not bearing a son.

00:21:00.940 --> 00:21:02.330 line:80%
You never favored her

00:21:03.050 --> 00:21:04.610 line:80%
and always beat and scolded her.

00:21:05.020 --> 00:21:07.660 line:80%
My grandfather and uncles
clashed with you several times.

00:21:07.660 --> 00:21:08.940 line:80%
You disliked them long ago.

00:21:08.940 --> 00:21:10.940 line:80%
How could you avenge them?

00:21:10.940 --> 00:21:13.500 line:80%
Grandfather worried about Mother and me,

00:21:13.500 --> 00:21:15.530 line:80%
brought us gifts,

00:21:15.530 --> 00:21:17.500 line:80%
and described the mountain terrain.

00:21:18.290 --> 00:21:20.740 line:80%
That's why you targeted Mount Qimu.

00:21:22.460 --> 00:21:23.570 line:80%
Yang Heying,

00:21:23.890 --> 00:21:26.330 line:80%
how did my grandfather and mother die?

00:21:26.330 --> 00:21:27.610 line:80%
Ungrateful girl.

00:21:29.290 --> 00:21:30.130 line:80%
Honey.

00:21:30.700 --> 00:21:31.540 line:80%
Yang Heying,

00:21:32.290 --> 00:21:34.050 line:80%
answer Xiaolan

00:21:34.460 --> 00:21:35.493 line:80%
before losing your temper.

00:21:36.980 --> 00:21:37.820 line:80%
Alright.

00:21:40.420 --> 00:21:41.260 line:80%
So, today,

00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:42.850 line:80%
you're determined

00:21:42.850 --> 00:21:44.610 line:80%
to pin this great crime on me.

00:21:45.610 --> 00:21:47.700 line:80%
But empty words mean nothing.

00:21:48.090 --> 00:21:49.980 line:80%
Without evidence, I won't admit it.

00:21:49.980 --> 00:21:50.820 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:21:51.850 --> 00:21:53.850 line:80%
you wouldn't coerce a confession, right?

00:21:55.570 --> 00:21:56.780 line:80%
Every house has its rules.

00:21:57.530 --> 00:21:58.610 line:80%
So does every sect.

00:21:59.330 --> 00:22:00.420 line:80%
If anyone in the Six Sects

00:22:00.420 --> 00:22:03.330 line:80%
truly committed such a heinous act,

00:22:03.780 --> 00:22:05.220 line:80%
I won't forgive them.

00:22:06.660 --> 00:22:08.500 line:80%
I've sent people to Mount Qimu

00:22:09.180 --> 00:22:10.570 line:80%
to investigate thoroughly.

00:22:11.290 --> 00:22:13.090 line:80%
With such a massive corpse slave setup,

00:22:13.810 --> 00:22:17.020 line:80%
they can't clear all traces.

00:22:17.020 --> 00:22:20.090 line:80%
Then I'll summon heroes

00:22:20.090 --> 00:22:21.090 line:80%
in the world

00:22:23.130 --> 00:22:24.570 line:80%
to confront you.

00:22:27.290 --> 00:22:28.130 line:80%
Alright.

00:22:29.530 --> 00:22:30.370 line:80%
I'll wait.

00:22:31.850 --> 00:22:32.690 line:80%
Let's go.

00:22:37.980 --> 00:22:38.820 line:80%
Miss Yang,

00:22:39.460 --> 00:22:40.940 line:80%
your father may have framed my father.

00:22:41.420 --> 00:22:42.500 line:80%
Such a great enmity ahead,

00:22:43.130 --> 00:22:44.940 line:80%
our union seems impossible.

00:22:45.780 --> 00:22:46.660 line:80%
The betrothal token...

00:22:51.980 --> 00:22:53.290 line:80%
Take it back.

00:22:56.940 --> 00:22:59.020 line:80%
I never wanted to marry you anyway.

00:23:06.500 --> 00:23:07.780 line:80%
Lord Yang acts recklessly.

00:23:08.740 --> 00:23:10.220 line:80%
Miss Yang is headstrong.

00:23:10.850 --> 00:23:12.460 line:80%
Yang Heying is no good.

00:23:13.090 --> 00:23:13.930 line:80%
What about you?

00:23:15.530 --> 00:23:16.479 line:80%
- Yuzhi.
- Why did you

00:23:16.490 --> 00:23:17.950 line:80%
accuse Father in front of everyone?

00:23:18.500 --> 00:23:19.340 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:23:19.890 --> 00:23:21.090 line:80%
I was deceived.

00:23:21.810 --> 00:23:22.650 line:80%
Do you remember?

00:23:23.370 --> 00:23:24.740 line:80%
Initially, I didn't want to speak.

00:23:24.740 --> 00:23:25.850 line:80%
You kept pressing,

00:23:26.290 --> 00:23:27.810 line:80%
so I revealed what I knew.

00:23:28.530 --> 00:23:29.660 line:80%
I didn't make it up.

00:23:30.020 --> 00:23:30.860 line:80%
If I had known,

00:23:32.020 --> 00:23:33.050 line:80%
I'd have kept quiet

00:23:33.420 --> 00:23:34.610 line:80%
and hidden everything.

00:23:37.980 --> 00:23:39.220 line:80%
Master Xiuzhi,

00:23:39.570 --> 00:23:40.530 line:80%
impressive.

00:23:40.890 --> 00:23:43.500 line:80%
You cleared yourself spotlessly.

00:23:43.810 --> 00:23:44.890 line:80%
Innocent indeed.

00:23:45.530 --> 00:23:46.420 line:80%
Then tomorrow,

00:23:46.700 --> 00:23:49.530 line:80%
I'll hire 100 storytellers

00:23:49.810 --> 00:23:52.130 line:80%
to spread the recent Guangtian events

00:23:52.530 --> 00:23:54.290 line:80%
far and wide,

00:23:55.220 --> 00:23:56.460 line:80%
showing everyone

00:23:57.050 --> 00:23:59.570 line:80%
how cunning

00:23:59.570 --> 00:24:01.330 line:80%
and despicable

00:24:01.330 --> 00:24:02.850 line:80%
the honorable Master Xiuzhi is.

00:24:02.850 --> 00:24:03.740 line:80%
Let's see

00:24:03.740 --> 00:24:05.050 line:80%
if you can still become

00:24:05.050 --> 00:24:06.370 line:80%
the Lord.

00:24:06.370 --> 00:24:08.610 line:80%
What a sharp-tongued girl.

00:24:09.130 --> 00:24:10.500 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:24:10.980 --> 00:24:13.290 line:80%
the Six Sects have coexisted

00:24:13.980 --> 00:24:15.370 line:80%
but acted independently

00:24:15.370 --> 00:24:17.180 line:80%
for 200 years.

00:24:18.420 --> 00:24:21.700 line:80%
If we interfere recklessly,

00:24:21.700 --> 00:24:23.290 line:80%
it may disrupt unity

00:24:23.290 --> 00:24:25.420 line:80%
and let the demonic sect take advantage.

00:24:25.420 --> 00:24:26.260 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:24:27.050 --> 00:24:28.890 line:80%
A pigeon letter from Luoying Valley says

00:24:29.740 --> 00:24:31.220 line:80%
Lord Song is gravely injured

00:24:31.220 --> 00:24:32.220 line:80%
and unconscious.

00:24:32.980 --> 00:24:34.050 line:80%
If that's true,

00:24:34.700 --> 00:24:36.290 line:80%
even if he's alive,

00:24:36.290 --> 00:24:40.130 line:80%
he may never sit as the Lord again.

00:24:41.090 --> 00:24:42.660 line:80%
Lord Song has only two sons.

00:24:43.290 --> 00:24:44.850 line:80%
By seniority and merit,

00:24:49.220 --> 00:24:50.530 line:80%
it should be Song Xiuzhi

00:24:50.530 --> 00:24:51.850 line:80%
to take the lord position.

00:24:55.090 --> 00:24:56.370 line:80%
I don't think he's suitable.

00:24:58.290 --> 00:24:59.500 line:80%
The most suitable is you.

00:24:59.500 --> 00:25:00.340 line:80%
You...

00:25:00.740 --> 00:25:02.130 line:80%
The investigation isn't over,

00:25:02.500 --> 00:25:03.810 line:80%
yet you're already anxious

00:25:03.810 --> 00:25:04.980 line:80%
to fight for the position?

00:25:04.980 --> 00:25:06.420 line:80%
Lord Qi, please judge this.

00:25:06.740 --> 00:25:08.130 line:80%
Our Guangtian affairs

00:25:08.130 --> 00:25:09.276 line:80%
are none of others' business.

00:25:09.700 --> 00:25:10.540 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:25:10.890 --> 00:25:11.730 line:80%
this matter

00:25:12.180 --> 00:25:13.500 line:80%
requires your decision.

00:25:17.330 --> 00:25:18.420 line:80%
Now that it's come to this,

00:25:19.740 --> 00:25:21.610 line:80%
let's follow the old Guangtian rules.

00:25:23.810 --> 00:25:25.500 line:80%
I'm willing to compete with Xiuzhi

00:25:27.180 --> 00:25:28.810 line:80%
to determine the next lord.

00:25:36.900 --> 00:25:39.820 line:80%
(Guangtian Sect)

00:25:40.700 --> 00:25:45.020 line:80%
(Desheng Hall)

00:25:59.460 --> 00:26:00.940 line:80%
Let the duel begin.

00:26:17.180 --> 00:26:18.020 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:26:19.370 --> 00:26:21.370 line:80%
Fengchi and I
just received news last night.

00:26:32.090 --> 00:26:33.850 line:80%
Yuzhi hasn't fully recovered

00:26:33.850 --> 00:26:34.780 line:80%
and was just poisoned.

00:26:35.090 --> 00:26:36.090 line:80%
This is too unfair.

00:26:37.500 --> 00:26:38.340 line:80%
By the way, Lingbo,

00:26:38.660 --> 00:26:40.420 line:80%
I heard you went
to Mount Qimu for clues.

00:26:40.660 --> 00:26:41.780 line:80%
Did you find any survivors?

00:26:44.500 --> 00:26:45.740 line:80%
Even a corpse slave would help.

00:26:46.530 --> 00:26:47.530 line:80%
Xingjia has the antidote.

00:26:47.770 --> 00:26:48.929 line:80%
If we find the corpse slaves,

00:26:48.940 --> 00:26:50.740 line:80%
we can learn the truth from them.

00:26:51.370 --> 00:26:52.220 line:80%
Everything was burned.

00:26:52.810 --> 00:26:53.700 line:80%
The whole mountain

00:26:53.700 --> 00:26:54.810 line:80%
was reduced to ashes.

00:26:55.090 --> 00:26:56.530 line:80%
When Lingbo and I arrived,

00:26:56.850 --> 00:26:58.370 line:80%
we only saw charred skeletons.

00:26:58.890 --> 00:27:00.660 line:80%
No idea how many people were gone.

00:27:00.980 --> 00:27:01.940 line:80%
Huangsha Gang

00:27:02.130 --> 00:27:04.180 line:80%
seems to have vanished overnight.

00:27:05.180 --> 00:27:06.370 line:80%
Among the bones,

00:27:07.660 --> 00:27:09.370 line:80%
there were even young kids.

00:27:10.660 --> 00:27:11.780 line:80%
The perpetrators

00:27:12.020 --> 00:27:13.740 line:80%
are more ruthless than the demonic sect.

00:27:44.610 --> 00:27:45.500 line:80%
Master,

00:27:45.500 --> 00:27:46.810 line:80%
a duel for the Lord

00:27:47.050 --> 00:27:48.090 line:80%
allows hidden weapons?

00:27:48.810 --> 00:27:49.660 line:80%
Why not?

00:27:50.290 --> 00:27:51.180 line:80%
A duel

00:27:51.530 --> 00:27:53.570 line:80%
naturally demands full effort.

00:28:10.610 --> 00:28:11.450 line:80%
Yuzhi!

00:28:12.460 --> 00:28:13.300 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:28:13.850 --> 00:28:14.740 line:80%
if you go up now,

00:28:15.090 --> 00:28:16.660 line:80%
Yuzhi will only be more embarrassed.

00:28:22.810 --> 00:28:23.650 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:28:24.130 --> 00:28:24.970 line:80%
it's over.

00:28:28.500 --> 00:28:29.740 line:80%
I'm outmatched.

00:28:30.020 --> 00:28:30.980 line:80%
The outcome is decided.

00:28:30.980 --> 00:28:31.890 line:80%
(Desheng Hall)

00:28:31.890 --> 00:28:33.020 line:80%
Song Xiuzhi

00:28:33.500 --> 00:28:36.220 line:80%
will become the next Lord.

00:28:37.530 --> 00:28:38.370 line:80%
Everyone,

00:28:40.420 --> 00:28:41.850 line:80%
any objections?

00:28:43.220 --> 00:28:44.370 line:80%
I'm outmatched.

00:28:45.460 --> 00:28:46.420 line:80%
Master,

00:28:46.420 --> 00:28:47.260 line:80%
let's go.

00:28:49.700 --> 00:28:50.570 line:80%
Today's defeat

00:28:50.980 --> 00:28:53.890 line:80%
will be the step
to tomorrow's improvement.

00:28:59.290 --> 00:29:00.420 line:80%
Farewell.

00:29:01.810 --> 00:29:02.850 line:80%
I hope you

00:29:04.460 --> 00:29:05.530 line:80%
take care of yourselves.

00:29:06.780 --> 00:29:07.620 line:80%
Goodbye.

00:29:08.610 --> 00:29:09.450 line:80%
Let's go.

00:29:18.370 --> 00:29:19.210 line:80%
As expected, he lost.

00:29:20.530 --> 00:29:21.810 line:80%
Song Yuzhi is a rising star

00:29:22.180 --> 00:29:24.020 line:80%
among the young generation
of the Six Sects.

00:29:24.610 --> 00:29:26.020 line:80%
But I had never heard

00:29:26.740 --> 00:29:28.130 line:80%
of Song Xiuzhi.

00:29:28.460 --> 00:29:29.300 line:80%
This battle

00:29:29.530 --> 00:29:31.660 line:80%
was a shocking rise to fame.

00:29:32.090 --> 00:29:33.220 line:80%
The opponent was prepared.

00:29:34.370 --> 00:29:36.020 line:80%
Song Yuzhi should've avoided it,

00:29:36.460 --> 00:29:37.850 line:80%
biding his time.

00:29:39.290 --> 00:29:40.130 line:80%
However...

00:29:40.460 --> 00:29:41.980 line:80%
Mr. Song

00:29:41.980 --> 00:29:43.500 line:80%
has lived an easy life,

00:29:43.500 --> 00:29:45.050 line:80%
admired by all since childhood.

00:29:45.500 --> 00:29:46.460 line:80%
This battle

00:29:46.460 --> 00:29:47.420 line:80%
was a lesson for him.

00:29:47.980 --> 00:29:49.980 line:80%
Mr. Song likely understood this,

00:29:50.570 --> 00:29:51.890 line:80%
but he couldn't let this strife

00:29:52.023 --> 00:29:53.212 line:80%
cause chaos in Guangtian Sect.

00:29:53.290 --> 00:29:54.330 line:80%
So, he reluctantly fought.

00:29:54.700 --> 00:29:55.700 line:80%
All in all,

00:29:55.700 --> 00:29:57.023 line:80%
it was mercy,

00:29:57.034 --> 00:29:58.260 line:80%
unfit for great responsibility.

00:29:59.610 --> 00:30:00.450 line:80%
Shangguan,

00:30:01.050 --> 00:30:02.290 line:80%
you seem off.

00:30:02.290 --> 00:30:03.163 line:80%
Which side are you on?

00:30:03.890 --> 00:30:05.130 line:80%
I'm just speaking fairly.

00:30:05.130 --> 00:30:05.980 line:80%
Don't you know

00:30:05.980 --> 00:30:07.050 line:80%
he had his eye on Miss Cai?

00:30:07.050 --> 00:30:07.750 line:80%
Now,

00:30:07.761 --> 00:30:08.810 line:80%
his family is in upheaval,

00:30:08.810 --> 00:30:10.020 line:80%
and he's lost to his brother.

00:30:10.020 --> 00:30:10.940 line:80%
A double misfortune.

00:30:11.480 --> 00:30:12.370 line:80%
What if

00:30:12.370 --> 00:30:13.980 line:80%
Miss Cai softens,

00:30:13.980 --> 00:30:15.500 line:80%
turning sympathy into...

00:30:27.090 --> 00:30:27.930 line:80%
Talkative.

00:30:28.700 --> 00:30:29.570 line:80%
Young Master,

00:30:29.570 --> 00:30:30.780 line:80%
I don't mean that.

00:30:31.740 --> 00:30:32.649 line:80%
Father,

00:30:32.660 --> 00:30:33.850 line:80%
they are clearly scheming.

00:30:33.850 --> 00:30:34.980 line:80%
And we just let it go?

00:30:35.370 --> 00:30:36.210 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:30:36.570 --> 00:30:38.420 line:80%
their boldness in public

00:30:38.420 --> 00:30:39.610 line:80%
means everyone present

00:30:39.610 --> 00:30:42.330 line:80%
is pretending ignorance.

00:30:43.020 --> 00:30:44.130 line:80%
They were likely bribed

00:30:44.130 --> 00:30:45.500 line:80%
by Uncle Song

00:30:45.500 --> 00:30:46.890 line:80%
and Song Xiuzhi.

00:30:47.500 --> 00:30:48.810 line:80%
I'm rarely at the sect.

00:30:49.740 --> 00:30:51.780 line:80%
Naturally, they are closer to Xiuzhi.

00:30:53.420 --> 00:30:54.740 line:80%
You weren't prepared; they were.

00:30:55.370 --> 00:30:56.570 line:80%
So, you'd lose out.

00:30:56.980 --> 00:30:57.850 line:80%
But for now,

00:30:58.090 --> 00:31:00.370 line:80%
we must first uncover the truth
of the corpse slaves.

00:31:01.460 --> 00:31:02.300 line:80%
As for this,

00:31:02.570 --> 00:31:03.410 line:80%
let's wait.

00:31:04.460 --> 00:31:06.290 line:80%
Master, Yang Heying has confessed.

00:31:06.980 --> 00:31:08.740 line:80%
The man in black taught him

00:31:08.740 --> 00:31:09.700 line:80%
the corpse slave method.

00:31:10.180 --> 00:31:12.570 line:80%
This man can meddle in all sects,

00:31:12.940 --> 00:31:14.180 line:80%
and in one night,

00:31:14.180 --> 00:31:16.290 line:80%
clean all traces in Mount Qimu.

00:31:16.940 --> 00:31:18.290 line:80%
He seems omnipotent,

00:31:18.660 --> 00:31:20.220 line:80%
yet his motives remain unknown.

00:31:20.530 --> 00:31:21.610 line:80%
Yu Hui escaped as well.

00:31:23.020 --> 00:31:24.610 line:80%
Could they be working together?

00:31:24.890 --> 00:31:26.370 line:80%
This is extremely complex.

00:31:27.050 --> 00:31:28.220 line:80%
I must return to the sect

00:31:28.610 --> 00:31:29.980 line:80%
to trace the full story.

00:31:31.420 --> 00:31:32.460 line:80%
What are your plans?

00:31:33.180 --> 00:31:34.020 line:80%
Master,

00:31:34.980 --> 00:31:36.160 line:80%
I want to go to Luoying Valley

00:31:36.460 --> 00:31:37.300 line:80%
to see my father.

00:31:38.700 --> 00:31:40.090 line:80%
I haven't been back for a long time.

00:31:40.780 --> 00:31:42.420 line:80%
I'll go with Yuzhi.

00:31:42.780 --> 00:31:43.526 line:80%
Good.

00:31:43.537 --> 00:31:45.050 line:80%
At least you have company on the road.

00:31:48.180 --> 00:31:49.020 line:80%
What about you two?

00:31:50.660 --> 00:31:52.290 line:80%
Will you continue your wander

00:31:52.290 --> 00:31:53.660 line:80%
or return?

00:31:53.660 --> 00:31:54.500 line:80%
- Return.
- Return.

00:32:10.500 --> 00:32:11.340 line:80%
Master,

00:32:11.660 --> 00:32:12.980 line:80%
I wish to formally propose

00:32:13.290 --> 00:32:14.530 line:80%
to marry Lingbo.

00:32:26.980 --> 00:32:28.050 line:80%
I know it's not

00:32:28.050 --> 00:32:29.180 line:80%
the best timing,

00:32:29.180 --> 00:32:30.220 line:80%
given Yuzhi just...

00:32:30.220 --> 00:32:31.060 line:80%
No.

00:32:31.780 --> 00:32:32.620 line:80%
I'm happy.

00:32:33.180 --> 00:32:34.020 line:80%
Congratulations.

00:32:35.460 --> 00:32:36.300 line:80%
Yes.

00:32:36.500 --> 00:32:37.570 line:80%
This is a joyous occasion.

00:32:38.290 --> 00:32:39.610 line:80%
Lovers finally unite.

00:32:39.850 --> 00:32:40.940 line:80%
When your wedding is set,

00:32:41.610 --> 00:32:42.883 line:80%
I'll demand a celebratory drink.

00:32:51.370 --> 00:32:52.210 line:80%
Father,

00:32:52.740 --> 00:32:53.580 line:80%
I know

00:32:54.290 --> 00:32:55.220 line:80%
I used to be willful,

00:32:55.850 --> 00:32:56.980 line:80%
but now I understand.

00:33:01.330 --> 00:33:02.180 line:80%
This past year,

00:33:02.700 --> 00:33:03.740 line:80%
whenever I was in danger,

00:33:04.180 --> 00:33:05.700 line:80%
Fengchi risked his life to save me.

00:33:07.780 --> 00:33:09.220 line:80%
He was the first

00:33:09.220 --> 00:33:11.020 line:80%
to value my life over his own.

00:33:14.420 --> 00:33:15.260 line:80%
I want to marry him.

00:33:31.290 --> 00:33:32.130 line:80%
This matter

00:33:32.850 --> 00:33:34.420 line:80%
must be approved

00:33:35.460 --> 00:33:37.130 line:80%
by your mother.

00:33:46.130 --> 00:33:46.980 line:80%
I have

00:33:49.660 --> 00:33:50.700 line:80%
no objection.

00:33:51.020 --> 00:33:51.860 line:80%
Wonderful.

00:33:52.090 --> 00:33:53.180 line:80%
I'll toast you with tea.

00:33:53.180 --> 00:33:54.020 line:80%
Congrats to you both.

00:33:54.740 --> 00:33:55.580 line:80%
Congratulations.

00:34:14.410 --> 00:34:15.270 line:80%
Thank you

00:34:15.270 --> 00:34:16.330 line:80%
for helping me that night.

00:34:19.620 --> 00:34:20.580 line:80%
You found out.

00:34:22.580 --> 00:34:24.580 line:80%
Is that why you called me here?

00:34:24.580 --> 00:34:26.330 line:80%
I came to bid farewell.

00:34:26.330 --> 00:34:28.060 line:80%
Where are you headed now?

00:34:30.890 --> 00:34:32.660 line:80%
Yang Heying killed my mother,

00:34:33.220 --> 00:34:34.930 line:80%
grandfather, and uncles.

00:34:36.140 --> 00:34:37.290 line:80%
I have no family left,

00:34:38.060 --> 00:34:40.180 line:80%
but I won't let them die in vain.

00:34:40.850 --> 00:34:42.180 line:80%
I plan to go to Huangsha Gang

00:34:42.180 --> 00:34:43.660 line:80%
to find out the truth,

00:34:43.660 --> 00:34:44.930 line:80%
gather evidence,

00:34:44.930 --> 00:34:45.970 line:80%
and avenge them.

00:34:49.410 --> 00:34:51.810 line:80%
Siqi Sect usually wields whips.

00:34:52.780 --> 00:34:54.290 line:80%
Why a blade?

00:34:54.810 --> 00:34:55.890 line:80%
Actually,

00:34:56.810 --> 00:34:58.450 line:80%
I admired Ms. Cai since childhood,

00:34:58.623 --> 00:35:00.692 line:80%
so I convinced my mother
to let me learn the blade.

00:35:00.850 --> 00:35:02.180 line:80%
Mother always indulged me,

00:35:02.620 --> 00:35:03.850 line:80%
so she let me.

00:35:05.370 --> 00:35:07.140 line:80%
Sadly, my talent was limited.

00:35:07.850 --> 00:35:09.700 line:80%
I couldn't protect her.

00:35:17.290 --> 00:35:18.620 line:80%
Since you admire Aunt,

00:35:19.220 --> 00:35:20.180 line:80%
you should know

00:35:20.930 --> 00:35:22.490 line:80%
why her blade is called

00:35:22.490 --> 00:35:23.490 line:80%
the Sunshine Blade.

00:35:27.700 --> 00:35:28.540 line:80%
Radiant sunshine

00:35:29.010 --> 00:35:29.930 line:80%
means brightness

00:35:30.740 --> 00:35:31.620 line:80%
and fearlessness.

00:35:32.290 --> 00:35:33.140 line:80%
Go do

00:35:33.140 --> 00:35:33.980 line:80%
what you want.

00:35:34.740 --> 00:35:35.780 line:80%
Your skills are strong.

00:35:37.100 --> 00:35:37.970 line:80%
I believe,

00:35:38.620 --> 00:35:39.740 line:80%
with time,

00:35:41.450 --> 00:35:43.700 line:80%
you'll carve your own path.

00:35:48.500 --> 00:35:53.100 line:80%
(Luoying Valley)

00:35:54.290 --> 00:35:55.850 line:80%
Your father survived

00:35:56.580 --> 00:35:57.780 line:80%
but lost all inner power.

00:35:58.100 --> 00:36:00.810 line:80%
He can only live as an ordinary man.

00:36:01.540 --> 00:36:03.660 line:80%
Did he say who harmed him?

00:36:04.370 --> 00:36:06.100 line:80%
He briefly regained consciousness once,

00:36:06.810 --> 00:36:09.290 line:80%
but he was delirious,

00:36:09.660 --> 00:36:11.220 line:80%
with toxin still inside.

00:36:12.370 --> 00:36:13.970 line:80%
He only shouted

00:36:14.580 --> 00:36:15.420 line:80%
"Unfilial"

00:36:15.970 --> 00:36:17.450 line:80%
and passed out again.

00:36:17.450 --> 00:36:18.700 line:80%
As for what happened,

00:36:19.220 --> 00:36:21.810 line:80%
we'll have to ask when he wakes up.

00:36:22.140 --> 00:36:23.410 line:80%
Thanks to you two.

00:36:23.970 --> 00:36:25.100 line:80%
You saved my father.

00:36:26.330 --> 00:36:27.170 line:80%
Otherwise...

00:36:30.970 --> 00:36:32.700 line:80%
I don't deserve to be
my father's disciple.

00:36:33.290 --> 00:36:35.410 line:80%
I almost couldn't save him.

00:36:36.100 --> 00:36:36.970 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:36:36.970 --> 00:36:37.970 line:80%
life is like this.

00:36:38.410 --> 00:36:39.810 line:80%
It isn't smooth sailing.

00:36:40.620 --> 00:36:42.540 line:80%
You haven't fully recovered,

00:36:42.750 --> 00:36:43.620 line:80%
and you've never

00:36:43.620 --> 00:36:45.740 line:80%
doubted your own brother.

00:36:47.620 --> 00:36:48.970 line:80%
You were unprepared.

00:36:49.580 --> 00:36:50.850 line:80%
That was unavoidable.

00:36:52.410 --> 00:36:53.250 line:80%
Exactly.

00:36:54.100 --> 00:36:56.330 line:80%
This would happen to anyone.

00:36:56.330 --> 00:36:57.290 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:36:57.740 --> 00:36:59.186 line:80%
Master is the head of the Six Sects.

00:36:59.290 --> 00:37:00.330 line:80%
He won't ignore this.

00:37:00.700 --> 00:37:01.970 line:80%
Once Song Xiuzhi's collusion

00:37:01.970 --> 00:37:04.100 line:80%
with Yang Heying is revealed,

00:37:04.930 --> 00:37:05.930 line:80%
no one will follow him.

00:37:08.660 --> 00:37:09.500 line:80%
Thanks, Lord Cai,

00:37:10.220 --> 00:37:11.060 line:80%
Zhao.

00:37:11.450 --> 00:37:13.850 line:80%
I must resolve Guangtian matters myself.

00:37:14.450 --> 00:37:15.620 line:80%
This loss was my fault,

00:37:16.700 --> 00:37:18.100 line:80%
but next time, I'll reclaim

00:37:18.540 --> 00:37:20.700 line:80%
the lord title openly.

00:37:36.020 --> 00:37:37.580 line:80%
(Tablet of Yulan, Late Mother)

00:37:37.580 --> 00:37:38.420 line:80%
Mother,

00:37:38.740 --> 00:37:40.370 line:80%
I had Yin Qinglian's spirit tablet

00:37:41.490 --> 00:37:43.010 line:80%
thrown into the waste pond.

00:37:43.410 --> 00:37:44.540 line:80%
Song Shijun had high hopes

00:37:45.100 --> 00:37:47.220 line:80%
for her son Song Yuzhi,

00:37:48.180 --> 00:37:50.140 line:80%
yet I defeated him.

00:37:50.140 --> 00:37:51.540 line:80%
That's true.

00:37:51.540 --> 00:37:52.380 line:80%
Who?

00:37:56.140 --> 00:37:56.980 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:37:57.410 --> 00:37:58.250 line:80%
Guards!

00:38:00.540 --> 00:38:01.540 line:80%
They won't make it.

00:38:07.780 --> 00:38:08.620 line:80%
Lord Song,

00:38:10.010 --> 00:38:11.010 line:80%
two questions for you.

00:38:11.330 --> 00:38:12.810 line:80%
Good and evil never coexist.

00:38:13.930 --> 00:38:16.140 line:80%
I have nothing to tell you.

00:38:16.490 --> 00:38:17.700 line:80%
Good and evil never coexist?

00:38:20.660 --> 00:38:22.330 line:80%
I haven't colluded with outsiders,

00:38:22.620 --> 00:38:23.780 line:80%
nor harmed my father

00:38:24.620 --> 00:38:25.620 line:80%
or brother.

00:38:26.290 --> 00:38:27.660 line:80%
Between us,

00:38:27.660 --> 00:38:28.500 line:80%
who's righteous,

00:38:29.220 --> 00:38:30.060 line:80%
and who's evil?

00:38:30.330 --> 00:38:31.620 line:80%
Yang Heying did it all.

00:38:31.810 --> 00:38:32.740 line:80%
Since I came,

00:38:33.140 --> 00:38:34.810 line:80%
I already know the full story.

00:38:35.490 --> 00:38:36.330 line:80%
Tell me.

00:38:36.780 --> 00:38:38.353 line:80%
Who taught you the corpse slave method,

00:38:38.780 --> 00:38:39.970 line:80%
wounded Song Shijun,

00:38:40.330 --> 00:38:42.330 line:80%
and helped you plan

00:38:43.330 --> 00:38:44.450 line:80%
the power grab?

00:38:49.580 --> 00:38:53.020 line:80%
(Tablet of Yulan, Late Mother)

00:38:55.370 --> 00:38:56.660 line:80%
Guangtian lords

00:38:57.490 --> 00:38:58.850 line:80%
took multiple concubines

00:38:59.700 --> 00:39:00.640 line:80%
and bore many children.

00:39:01.370 --> 00:39:03.620 line:80%
Since Yin Qinglian married Song Shijun,

00:39:04.220 --> 00:39:05.450 line:80%
she had no more children.

00:39:05.780 --> 00:39:07.740 line:80%
Even the concubines vanished.

00:39:08.180 --> 00:39:09.580 line:80%
Did that person tell you

00:39:09.930 --> 00:39:11.970 line:80%
Yin Qinglian killed them all?

00:39:13.850 --> 00:39:14.890 line:80%
Yes.

00:39:24.180 --> 00:39:25.810 line:80%
Mother was just a maid.

00:39:26.780 --> 00:39:28.410 line:80%
She was ordered to serve the Lord.

00:39:29.010 --> 00:39:30.290 line:80%
Would she dare refuse?

00:39:32.810 --> 00:39:34.180 line:80%
She did nothing wrong.

00:39:34.620 --> 00:39:36.700 line:80%
Yin Qinglian poisoned her,

00:39:36.700 --> 00:39:38.010 line:80%
torturing her to death.

00:39:38.620 --> 00:39:39.810 line:80%
If it weren't for the letter

00:39:39.810 --> 00:39:41.290 line:80%
hidden in her pillow,

00:39:43.220 --> 00:39:44.410 line:80%
I'd still be in the dark.

00:39:44.930 --> 00:39:46.370 line:80%
Was it Li Wenxun,

00:39:47.580 --> 00:39:48.660 line:80%
or someone else

00:39:49.060 --> 00:39:51.010 line:80%
from the Six Sects?

00:39:54.620 --> 00:39:55.660 line:80%
Now, I no longer need

00:39:56.970 --> 00:39:58.810 line:80%
to hide from that person,

00:39:59.290 --> 00:40:00.810 line:80%
but I truly don't know who they were.

00:40:01.220 --> 00:40:02.486 line:80%
Their skills were extraordinary,

00:40:02.740 --> 00:40:04.013 line:80%
their movements were ghost-like,

00:40:04.220 --> 00:40:05.850 line:80%
and their bodies were covered.

00:40:07.140 --> 00:40:08.850 line:80%
I couldn't gauge
their martial arts origin.

00:40:13.330 --> 00:40:14.580 line:80%
That's it?

00:40:18.490 --> 00:40:19.740 line:80%
You were just a pawn.

00:40:20.140 --> 00:40:21.180 line:80%
Nothing more to learn.

00:40:21.740 --> 00:40:23.140 line:80%
Pay respects to your mother.

00:40:24.180 --> 00:40:25.490 line:80%
Such a good cover

00:40:25.890 --> 00:40:26.970 line:80%
deserves use.

00:40:26.970 --> 00:40:27.890 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:40:31.810 --> 00:40:33.220 line:80%
You conspired with Uncle Song,

00:40:33.850 --> 00:40:35.580 line:80%
scheming for ten years.

00:40:36.180 --> 00:40:38.010 line:80%
Whether your mother
was poisoned or not,

00:40:38.540 --> 00:40:40.490 line:80%
you'd still go after the lord position.

00:40:40.890 --> 00:40:41.930 line:80%
The man in black

00:40:41.930 --> 00:40:44.060 line:80%
just provided a convenient excuse.

00:40:46.060 --> 00:40:47.700 line:80%
Power, once gained,

00:40:48.850 --> 00:40:50.290 line:80%
you should hold tightly.

00:40:57.060 --> 00:40:58.620 line:80%
Our guess was correct.

00:40:59.290 --> 00:41:01.140 line:80%
The man in black was indeed
from the Six Sects,

00:41:01.140 --> 00:41:03.450 line:80%
hence knowing Song secrets.

00:41:03.450 --> 00:41:04.290 line:80%
However,

00:41:04.450 --> 00:41:05.620 line:80%
after all these plots,

00:41:06.140 --> 00:41:07.010 line:80%
what is their goal?

00:41:08.570 --> 00:41:09.410 line:80%
Young Master,

00:41:09.410 --> 00:41:10.330 line:80%
should we

00:41:10.330 --> 00:41:11.620 line:80%
tell Miss Cai?

00:41:12.620 --> 00:41:13.460 line:80%
Not yet.

00:41:15.580 --> 00:41:16.420 line:80%
Young Master,

00:41:16.890 --> 00:41:17.803 line:80%
everything is prepared.

00:41:18.370 --> 00:41:19.660 line:80%
Was the message spread?

00:41:20.490 --> 00:41:21.410 line:80%
Young Master,

00:41:21.410 --> 00:41:23.140 line:80%
with so many treasures,

00:41:23.140 --> 00:41:24.450 line:80%
are you buying a city

00:41:24.450 --> 00:41:26.290 line:80%
or building a new treasury?

00:41:26.290 --> 00:41:27.130 line:80%
To Luoying Valley.

00:41:40.780 --> 00:41:42.010 line:80%
You had a dream?

00:41:48.220 --> 00:41:49.330 line:80%
I dreamed of Aunt.

00:41:51.780 --> 00:41:52.620 line:80%
Cai Han,

00:41:53.180 --> 00:41:54.330 line:80%
a year without seeing you,

00:41:54.780 --> 00:41:55.850 line:80%
why are you so thin?

00:41:56.780 --> 00:41:57.780 line:80%
Not eating well?

00:41:58.180 --> 00:42:00.620 line:80%
No, I missed you.

00:42:01.180 --> 00:42:02.930 line:80%
You even became a demoness.

00:42:04.290 --> 00:42:05.330 line:80%
Are you impressed

00:42:05.330 --> 00:42:06.370 line:80%
and happy

00:42:06.370 --> 00:42:07.290 line:80%
about that?

00:42:07.290 --> 00:42:08.810 line:80%
Yes.

00:42:08.810 --> 00:42:09.890 line:80%
You're amazing.

00:42:11.490 --> 00:42:12.540 line:80%
But Zhao,

00:42:13.220 --> 00:42:15.010 line:80%
why did you elope with Ning

00:42:15.010 --> 00:42:17.060 line:80%
and bring back Yuzhi?

00:42:17.700 --> 00:42:19.180 line:80%
Yuzhi is handsome,

00:42:19.180 --> 00:42:20.473 line:80%
and you don't need confinement.

00:42:20.930 --> 00:42:22.100 line:80%
Eloping, my foot!

00:42:22.580 --> 00:42:24.700 line:80%
I was righting
an injustice and saved him.

00:42:24.970 --> 00:42:26.180 line:80%
There's plenty of injustice.

00:42:26.450 --> 00:42:27.740 line:80%
Why save only him?

00:42:28.220 --> 00:42:29.490 line:80%
Stop showing off.

00:42:30.970 --> 00:42:31.810 line:80%
Where's Yuzhi?

00:42:31.810 --> 00:42:33.330 line:80%
He worked so hard.

00:42:33.330 --> 00:42:35.450 line:80%
He was with Lord Song last night.

00:42:35.450 --> 00:42:36.330 line:80%
At the early Mao hour,

00:42:36.330 --> 00:42:37.796 line:80%
he was already practicing.

00:42:38.010 --> 00:42:39.700 line:80%
Almost six hours already.

00:42:42.620 --> 00:42:43.640 line:80%
Zhao, where are you going?

00:42:43.780 --> 00:42:44.780 line:80%
To find Yuzhi.

00:42:54.180 --> 00:42:55.980 line:80%
(Wonton)

00:43:01.060 --> 00:43:02.100 line:80%
Hello.

00:43:03.620 --> 00:43:04.460 line:80%
Here.

00:43:04.620 --> 00:43:07.060 line:80%
Authentic Spring Tofu Pudding. Try it.

00:43:07.810 --> 00:43:08.660 line:80%
Thank you, Uncle.

00:43:08.660 --> 00:43:09.500 line:80%
I've eaten already.

00:43:12.410 --> 00:43:15.140 line:80%
After all these years,
you're the first man

00:43:15.140 --> 00:43:17.220 line:80%
Manager Zhao brought back.

00:43:20.330 --> 00:43:21.556 line:80%
Do you want to marry into here?

00:43:24.370 --> 00:43:26.330 line:80%
Stop joking.

00:43:26.330 --> 00:43:28.220 line:80%
Yuzhi is a prodigy.

00:43:28.780 --> 00:43:31.220 line:80%
All the Six Sects will be under him.

00:43:31.620 --> 00:43:33.740 line:80%
How could we keep him here?

00:43:38.290 --> 00:43:39.450 line:80%
Another bowl, Uncle Douhua.

00:43:42.970 --> 00:43:44.220 line:80%
Someone barged in here!

00:43:44.220 --> 00:43:45.060 line:80%
Come with me!

00:43:47.100 --> 00:43:48.220 line:80%
Let's go.

00:43:50.100 --> 00:43:50.940 line:80%
Make way.

00:43:55.450 --> 00:43:56.290 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:43:56.890 --> 00:43:57.780 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:43:58.010 --> 00:43:58.850 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:43:59.340 --> 00:44:00.220 line:80%
the Young Master

00:44:00.220 --> 00:44:02.580 line:80%
came here to propose.

00:44:05.561 --> 00:44:16.221 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:44:34.981 --> 00:44:39.391 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:44:39.956 --> 00:44:44.571 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:44:44.911 --> 00:44:49.476 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:44:50.001 --> 00:44:54.301 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:44:57.246 --> 00:45:01.946 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:45:02.471 --> 00:45:06.761 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:45:07.421 --> 00:45:11.451 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:45:11.766 --> 00:45:16.891 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:45:17.466 --> 00:45:22.276 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:45:22.491 --> 00:45:26.661 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:45:27.386 --> 00:45:31.321 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:45:31.821 --> 00:45:37.096 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:45:59.826 --> 00:46:04.956 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:46:05.321 --> 00:46:09.691 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:46:09.956 --> 00:46:14.086 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:46:14.271 --> 00:46:19.846 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪